<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎌 神戶環球影城親子慶生之旅 🎂</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        /* 背景動畫元素 */
        .bg-animation {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        /* 櫻花飄落動畫 */
        .sakura {
            position: absolute;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffb7d5 0%, #ff69b4 100%);
            border-radius: 50% 0 50% 0;
            animation: fall linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        @keyframes fall {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg);
            }
        }
        
        /* 雲朵飄動 */
        .cloud {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 100px;
            animation: cloudFloat linear infinite;
        }
        
        .cloud::before, .cloud::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 100px;
        }
        
        @keyframes cloudFloat {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-200px);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateX(calc(100vw + 200px));
            }
        }
        
        /* 富士山背景 */
        .fuji-mountain {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 300px solid transparent;
            border-right: 300px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 200px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .fuji-mountain::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50px;
            left: -250px;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 250px solid transparent;
            border-right: 250px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 150px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }
        
        /* 主容器 */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        /* 標題區 */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #c06c84 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '🎌';
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 100px;
            opacity: 0.1;
            top: -20px;
            left: 20px;
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }
        
        .header::after {
            content: '🗾';
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 100px;
            opacity: 0.1;
            bottom: -20px;
            right: 20px;
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite reverse;
        }
        
        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                transform: translateY(-100px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .header .subtitle {
            color: #fff5f5;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: 400;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        /* 資訊卡片 */
        .info-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
            border: 3px solid #ff6b9d;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                transform: translateY(30px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        
        .info-card h2 {
            color: #ff6b9d;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .info-card h3 {
            color: #c06c84;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        /* 日程卡片 */
        .day-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeef8 0%, #fff5f5 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.2);
            border: 3px solid #ff6b9d;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .day-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.3);
        }
        
        .day-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .day-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .day-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .day-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .day-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .day-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        
        .day-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #c06c84 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        /* 時間軸 */
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .timeline-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, white 0%, #fff5f5 100%);
        }
        
        .time {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff6b9d;
            min-width: 120px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .activity {
            flex: 1;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .note {
            color: #c06c84;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-left: 120px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        /* 提示框 */
        .tip-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6 0%, #ffe4b3 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #ffb347;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .tip-box h4 {
            color: #ff8c00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .tip-box ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .tip-box li {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        /* 特殊標記 */
        .birthday-mark {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #ff1493 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-left: 10px;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.4);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.6);
            }
        }
        
        /* 表格樣式 */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #c06c84 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        tr:hover {
            background: #fff5f5;
        }
        
        /* 按鈕樣式 */
        .print-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #c06c84 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 20px auto;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .print-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.6);
        }
        
        /* 頁尾 */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        /* 響應式設計 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
            
            .day-card {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .timeline-item {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .time {
                min-width: auto;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
            
            .note {
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
        
        /* 列印樣式 */
        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
            }
            
            .bg-animation,
            .fuji-mountain,
            .print-btn {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .day-card,
            .info-card {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 背景動畫 -->
    <div class="bg-animation" id="bgAnimation"></div>
    
    <!-- 富士山背景 -->
    <div class="fuji-mountain"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 標題 -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎌 2026年6月 神戶環球影城親子慶生之旅 🎂</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">⏱️ 5天4夜 | 👨‍👩‍👧 2位大人 + 1位6歲小孩（生日6/13）</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 航班資訊 -->
        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>✈️ 航班資訊</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>航段</th>
                    <th>日期</th>
                    <th>航班</th>
                    <th>時間</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>🛫 去程</td>
                    <td>2026/6/11（四）</td>
                    <td>樂桃 MM032</td>
                    <td>高雄小港 14:45 → 大阪關西 18:30</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>🛬 回程</td>
                    <td>2026/6/15（日）</td>
                    <td>樂桃 MM031</td>
                    <td>大阪關西 11:05 → 高雄小港 13:50</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 住宿資訊 -->
        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>🏨 住宿資訊</h2>
            <h3>📍 6/11-6/13（3晚）</h3>
            <p style="padding-left: 20px;">Remm Plus Kobe 神戶三宮</p>
            <h3>📍 6/14（1晚）</h3>
            <p style="padding-left: 20px;">Odysis Suites Osaka Airport Hotel</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Day 1 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-header">📅 Day 1 - 6/11（四）抵達神戶</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">14:45</div>
                <div class="activity">🛫 高雄小港機場起飛</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">18:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🛬 抵達關西機場（日本時間）</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">18:30-19:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🛃 入境、領行李</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">19:30-20:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🚶 前往神戶高速船乘船處</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">📍 關西機場第一航廈1F</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">20:00-20:30</div>
                <div class="activity">⛴️ 搭乘高速船往神戶機場</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚢 神戶-關空Bay Shuttle</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">20:30-21:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🚇 神戶機場→三宮站</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚈 搭Port Liner</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">21:00-21:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🏨 步行至飯店CHECK IN</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🏢 Remm Plus Kobe</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">21:30-22:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🍜 晚餐：すき家Sukiya 三宮店</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">⏰ 24小時營業，適合晚到</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">22:30~</div>
                <div class="activity">😴 回飯店休息</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">💤 早點休息準備明天環球影城</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Day 2 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-header">📅 Day 2 - 6/12（五）大阪環球影城 USJ 🎢</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">06:30-07:20</div>
                <div class="activity">🍳 飯店早餐、準備出發</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">👶 記得攜帶嬰兒車</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">07:40</div>
                <div class="activity">🚌 三宮巴士站發車</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🎯 往USJ直達巴士</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">08:18</div>
                <div class="activity">🎉 抵達環球影城</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">⚡ 視情況可能提早開園</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">08:18-08:30</div>
                <div class="activity">📸 入園準備、拍照</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">08:30-12:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🎮 上午遊玩</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🏃 建議先玩熱門設施</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">12:30-13:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🍔 午餐</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🍽️ 園區內餐廳</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">13:30-18:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🎡 下午遊玩</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">👶 小孩可在嬰兒車休息</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">18:00-19:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🍕 晚餐</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🍽️ 園區內餐廳</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">19:00-20:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🎪 繼續遊玩/購物</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">20:10</div>
                <div class="activity">🚌 USJ巴士站發車</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🏠 回三宮</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">20:50</div>
                <div class="activity">🏁 抵達三宮巴士站</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">21:00~</div>
                <div class="activity">😴 回飯店休息</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tip-box">
                <h4>🎯 建議事項</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>💳 建議購買快速通關券（小孩體力有限）</li>
                    <li>📱 下載USJ官方APP查看即時等候時間</li>
                    <li>☂️ 攜帶防曬用品、水壺、雨具</li>
                    <li>👶 嬰兒車可在園區租借或自帶</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Day 3 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-header">📅 Day 3 - 6/13（六）姬路城+明石海峽大橋+生田神社 <span class="birthday-mark">🎂 生日快樂！</span></div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">08:00-08:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🍳 飯店早餐</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">08:45</div>
                <div class="activity">🚄 三宮站出發</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚆 JR神戶線新快速</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">09:25</div>
                <div class="activity">🏁 抵達姬路站</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">⏱️ 車程約40分鐘</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">09:30-09:50</div>
                <div class="activity">🚶 步行至姬路城</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">📍 約1.5公里，20分鐘</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">09:50-12:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🏯 參觀姬路城</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🎌 天守閣、西之丸庭園</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">12:30-13:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🍖 午餐：豚屋豚一 姫路站前店</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚶 步行回車站途中</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">13:45</div>
                <div class="activity">🚄 姬路站發車</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚆 JR神戶線</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">14:15</div>
                <div class="activity">🏁 抵達舞子站</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">⏱️ 車程約30分鐘</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">14:20-15:30</div>
                <div class="activity">🌉 明石海峽大橋</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🎫 舞子海上步道（門票¥250）</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">15:30-15:45</div>
                <div class="activity">🌳 舞子公園散步</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">📸 可看大橋全景</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">16:00</div>
                <div class="activity">🚄 舞子站發車</div>
            </div>
            <div class="note">🚆 JR神戶線</div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="time">16:20</div>
                <div class="activity">🏁 抵達三宮站</div>
